data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Welcome to your new home in the highly desirable DeBary Fllorida community! This charming 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence boasts a 2-car garage and is nestled on a spacious 1/4 acre lot with an expansive fenced yard – and the best part? No HOA! The main living area of this home is adorned with plank vinyl tile flooring, adding a touch of elegance and easy maintenance to your daily living spaces as well as a wood burning fireplace. The hall bath is equipped with a relaxing jetted tub offering a spa-like experience within the comfort of your own home. Step out to the oversized screened lanai, the perfect spot for enjoying the Florida sunshine or entertaining guests in a bug-free environment. The layout of this home provides endless possibilities, especially with the flex space off the kitchen. It's ideal for a home office, playroom, or whatever suits your lifestyle. The large fenced yard is a true gem, providing ample space for gardening, pets, and various outdoor activities. It's a private oasis for you to enjoy. Enjoy cost-effective utility options with a well and septic system, providing both sustainability and efficiency. This home is conveniently located near shopping, medical facilities, and offers easy access to I4, making your daily commute a breeze. Benefit from a 2019 roof and a 2012 AC unit, and hurricane shudders ensuring comfort and peace of mind. You can also leverage your financing using Renovation lending that combines with all loan types (FHA 203K, VA Renovation, Fannie Mae HomeStyle, Freddie Mac Choice) which will allow you take a house you like, and turn it into a home you will love. Update the kitchen, bathrooms, paint and so much more. Call me for more details.
